title: Hello This is John
description:
John has the answers to all our questions (00:11:02). Kyle Rittenhouse makes an appearance on a Blaze podcast You Are Here (00:12:02). Jussie Smollett cranked it with one of his "attackers" (00:18:00). Quantum Week Chris released his trailer for "At a Theater Near Me" and the guys are concerned about the strategy behind it (00:34:45). Transgender swimmer at UPenn is dominating (00:59:13). Kirk admits to a studio (possibly life) habit (01:21:40) & much more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
